Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"Higor",
    "email" : "Higor@gmail.com",
    "password" : "123456"
}

### Login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/game/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "Higor",
    "email": "Higor@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456",
    "rol" : "comprador"
}

